&nbsp;
There are in total 17 people surveyed and 3 companies (Visibilia Editore, Visibilia srl in liquidazione e Visibilia Editrice) the recipients of the notice of closing investigations signed by the prosecutor Laura Pedio and the substitutes Marina Gravina and Luigi Luzi. The disputed offences, in various ways, are false social communications and false social communications of listed societies. The current partner Dimitri Kuntz D'Habsburg Lorena and the previous Canio Mazzaro, his sister Fiorella Garnero and his nephew Silvia Garnero are also investigated. All of them had roles in the board of directors of Visibilia Editore in the period between 2014 and 2023.
&nbsp;
<h2>Pm, Santanchè and others hid losses
Daniela Santanchè and the other investigators would have hidden to the public the "losses" of the company Visibilia Editore and obtained a "unjust profit". Santanchè "as an advisor, managing director and president", and the other co-inquired "knowly exhibited", in violation of the articles of the civil code, "in the financial statements of the company" Visibilia Editore from 2016 to 2022 "the relations or other social communications directed to the members or the public made material relevant not to the truth, in a concretely suitable way to induce others in error". This is what the Prosecutor of Milan writes in the notice of closing the preliminary investigations in which false crimes are hypothesized in the budget for the company share in stock on the Euronext Growth Milan. By doing so - according to the investigations of the economic-financial police core of the GdF in Milan and the Pedio-Gravina-Luzi pm - they would have achieved "an unfair profit (prosecution of the business activity by hiding the losses to the public, avoiding both the necessary costly recapitalization, and the purely 'conservative' management.
&nbsp;
<h2>Pm, systematic inability to produce income.
In the notice of closing the investigations on Visibilia Editore, the Procura di Milano speaks of "systematic inability of the corporate complex to produce income using optimistic industrial plans - approved by the company's cda - that contained operating income forecasts (difference between the value of production and the cost of production) never respected, with significant negative shocks between the forecast results and the agreed results". &nbsp;
&nbsp;
<h2>Daniela Santanchè, I have nothing to comment on
"I have nothing to say and say." He told Syracuse the Minister of Tourism Daniela Santanchè after the news of the closure of the investigations of the Prosecure of Milan that has in hand the file of investigation on the dissesto of Visibilia. To the minister, who is investigated, the pm contest false in the budget. The minister opened to the castle Maniace of Syracuse the general states of Cinema that will be held in the Sicilian city until 14 April.

