&nbsp; 
Durante l'esecuzione del provvedimento emesso dall'autorità giudiziaria sono state sottoposte a sequestro tutte le attrezzature utilizzate per gli interventi quali i bisturi, estrattori, una poltrona professionale e attrezzatura per radiografie>, in modo da impedire che l'attività illecitamente esercitata dal falso dentista "potesse - viene spiegato in una nota - continuare a mettere a repentaglio la salute di ulteriori ignari pazienti". Il responsabile è stato denunciato alla Procura della Repubblica di Ferrara in quanto ritenuto colpevole del reato di esercizio abusivo di professione medica.

en_content:
AGI -&nbsp;The Finance Guard of Ferrara seized an outpatient where, according to the accusations, the dental activity was illegally exercised. According to the financiers, inside there was a dental technician who, despite never obtaining a degree in medicine and other qualification, exercised abusively the profession, also getting to practice anesthetics to patients.
&nbsp;
During the execution of the measure issued by the judicial authority, all the equipment used for interventions such as scalpels, extractors, a professional armchair and radiograph equipment > were subjected to kidnapping, so as to prevent the activity unlawfully exercised by the false dentist "may - it is explained in a note - continue to jeopardize the health of other ignorant patients". The person responsible has been denounced to the Prosecutor of the Republic of Ferrara as he is deemed guilty of the offence of medical profession.
